translations: n.公主（princess 的复数形式）；王妃

phrs.translation: n. 将继承王位的公主；女王储
小公主（原著为小说，后多次改编为电影、电视剧和动画）
幽灵公主；魔法公主（动画电影）

sentences.sentence: All Disney princesses can get out of difficulty and find happiness by themselves.
sentences.translation: 所有的迪士尼公主都可以自己走出困境，找到幸福。

sentences.sentence: Princes and princesses have day-jobs and ride bicycles, not horses (or helicopters) .
sentences.translation: 王子和公主都有日常工作，他们骑自行车出行，而不是骑马（或乘直升机）出行。

sentences.sentence: One of the princesses went into each boat, and the soldier stepped into the same boat with the youngest.
sentences.translation: 每一位公主分别上了一条船，士兵和最小的公主上了同一条船。
